54
00:03:13,340 --> 00:03:14,580
No need. I'll go by myself.

55
00:03:16,060 --> 00:03:17,420
Take a good rest on the plane.

56
00:03:18,820 --> 00:03:19,500
Okay.

57
00:03:19,820 --> 00:03:20,660
You don't have to see me off. I'm leaving.

58
