The manager didn't inform us.

106
00:05:37,340 --> 00:05:38,820
I don't know where you'll sit.

107
00:05:42,780 --> 00:05:44,020
Is this desk taken?

108
00:05:44,700 --> 00:05:45,460
I don't think so.

109
00:05:46,130 --> 00:05:46,970
Thanks.

110
00:05:51,980 --> 00:05:53,460
The company's computers have individual locks,

111
00:05:53,659 --> 00:05:54,780
so you can't access them.

112
00:05:56,780 --> 00:05:58,460
This is our company's one and only chief designer,

113
00:05:58,659 --> 00:05:59,780
Ms. Hu Dexiang.

114
00:05:59,900 --> 00:06:01,460
I'm not the only one now.

115
00:06:01,700 --> 00:06:03,700
Ms. Jiang is also here to be a chief designer, right?

116
00:06:05,250 --> 00:06:05,900
Hello.

117
00:06:06,020 --> 00:06:07,140
I'm Hu Dexiang.

118
00:06:08,900 --> 00:06:10,140
I'm still a newcomer.

119
00:06:10,340 --> 00:06:11,580
Nice to meet you, Ms. Hu.

120
00:06:11,780 --> 00:06:13,580
You too. We're colleagues now.

121
00:06:13,780 --> 00:06:14,980
You can use my computer.

122
00:06:15,140 --> 00:06:15,900
Thank you.

123
00:06:16,020 --> 00:06:16,900
It's okay.

124
00:06:17,100 --> 00:06:18,020
I can do it myself.

125
00:06:18,220 --> 00:06:19,100
Here.

126
00:06:24,780 --> 00:06:27,140
She's Jiang Tian, the one who transferred from Beijing?

127
00:06:28,100 --> 00:06:29,780
Didn't they say she'd be here tomorrow?

128
00:06:29,900 --> 00:06:31,020
Don't ask me.

129
00:06:31,260 --> 00:06:32,659
I know nothing.

130
00:06:32,780 --> 00:06:33,460
Now,

131
00:06:33,700 --> 00:06:35,140
I just want to go home.

132
00:06:36,220 --> 00:06:37,340
There's a rumor.

133
00:06:37,700 --> 00:06:38,700
I don't know if it's true.

134
00:06:38,820 --> 00:06:39,900
What rumor?

135
00:06:40,460 --> 00:06:42,340
She was transferred to our company for promotion,

136
00:06:42,700 --> 00:06:44,330
but it's actually a demotion.

137
00:06:44,460 --> 00:06:45,580
Really?

138
00:07:03,020 --> 00:07:03,700
Ms. Hu,

139
00:07:04,340 --> 00:07:05,140
are you in a hurry?

140
00:07:05,660 --> 00:07:07,580
I'm not in a hurry, but I have to go.

141
00:07:08,020 --> 00:07:09,340
By the way, have you done rendering?

142
00:07:09,780 --> 00:07:10,540
Yes.

143
00:07:13,020 --> 00:07:14,220
If you're not in a hurry,

144
00:07:14,660 --> 00:07:15,980
could you please stay a little longer?

145
00:07:16,580 --> 00:07:18,020
After all, it's your computer,

146
00:07:18,460 --> 00:07:19,580
you'd better keep an eye on it.

147
00:07:21,140 --> 00:07:22,700
Would you do something bad?

148
00:07:24,700 --> 00:07:26,340
There's no important file in this computer, right?

149
00:07:27,020 --> 00:07:29,460
Who puts regular files in the company computer?

150
00:07:30,140 --> 00:07:31,020
So I'm curious

151
00:07:31,140 --> 00:07:32,250
why you said that?

152
00:07:33,580 --> 00:07:35,020
I just think it's inappropriate for you

153
00:07:35,140 --> 00:07:36,140
to leave like this.

154
00:07:36,260 --> 00:07:37,580
After all, we just met.

155
00:07:37,700 --> 00:07:38,460
You don't know

156
00:07:38,540 --> 00:07:39,580
what kind of person I am.

157
00:07:41,020 --> 00:07:43,020
You can't say I don't know at all.

158
00:07:43,460 --> 00:07:45,020
After all, I've heard about

159
00:07:45,220 --> 00:07:46,380
why you came here.

160
00:07:49,220 --> 00:07:50,140
Good news never go out.

161
00:07:50,220 --> 00:07:51,340
Bad news spread everywhere.

162
00:07:52,340 --> 00:07:53,340
Ms. Hu, where do you live?

163
00:07:53,700 --> 00:07:54,380
Beiwen River.

164
00:07:54,820 --> 00:07:55,700
It’s on my way home.

165
00:07:55,780 --> 00:07:56,659
How about this?

166
00:07:56,780 --> 00:07:58,220
I'll take a taxi and send you home later.

167
00:07:58,580 --> 00:07:59,460
What do you think?

