221
00:12:04,820 --> 00:12:06,060
If you don't answer my question,

222
00:12:06,180 --> 00:12:07,180
I'll call the police

223
00:12:07,500 --> 00:12:08,580
and sue you for trespassing.

224
00:12:08,820 --> 00:12:10,940
Fine, go ahead.

225
00:12:11,580 --> 00:12:13,620
I also want to ask the police for justice.

226
00:12:14,460 --> 00:12:15,500
Ms. Wu.

227
00:12:17,220 --> 00:12:17,460
Jiang.

228
00:12:17,500 --> 00:12:18,980
Did you drop something?

229
00:12:19,340 --> 00:12:20,100
Is this your reading glasses?

230
00:12:20,100 --> 00:12:21,220
Thank you. Here.

231
00:12:21,220 --> 00:12:22,340
-I brought it to you.
-You came at the right time.

232
00:12:23,420 --> 00:12:24,460
You can be the judge.

233
00:12:24,580 --> 00:12:26,220
A strange girl came here.

234
00:12:26,340 --> 00:12:27,700
She scratched my car

235
00:12:27,820 --> 00:12:30,100
and insisted that the house was hers.

236
00:12:30,180 --> 00:12:31,740
Come on, prove it.

237
00:12:31,860 --> 00:12:34,460
Tian, why are you back?

238
00:12:34,580 --> 00:12:36,220
You didn't even tell me.

