245
00:13:08,620 --> 00:13:09,700
My bad.

246
00:13:10,060 --> 00:13:11,700
I didn't handle it properly.

247
00:13:12,700 --> 00:13:15,340
But Tian, what's done is done.

248
00:13:15,610 --> 00:13:17,220
