00:14:26,220 --> 00:14:26,940
Ms. Wu,

277
00:14:28,340 --> 00:14:29,620
please move out.

278
00:14:31,620 --> 00:14:33,740
Sorry. I can't.

279
00:14:40,090 --> 00:14:41,940
Ms. Wu, you live alone, right?

